13 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
14 the members of this body join in honoring the life and memory of Artword Howard and
15 express their deepest and most sincere regret at his passing.
16 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
17 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
18 family of Artword Howard.
